        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/condi-virtuoso/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Condition Virtuoso is a simple to play, press skills off cooldown build that excels at dealing ranged damage.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build is also capable of doing large amounts of CC, and has multiple skills that can be swapped around for more utility, making it an excellent build for almost all bosses and situations.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is also relatively sturdy for a DPS build, and has good HP self sustain.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;gearing&quot;&gt;Gearing&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt; &lt;em&gt;There are multiple gear combinations that will arrive at the same total value of stats. However, we will be copying the gear that Snow Crows uses as that is most widely used.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; &lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
